# auto makes liga for ra-ethiopic and ga-ethiopic font = Glyphs.font
for layer in font.selectedLayers: print(layer.parent.name) name = layer.parent.name[:-5] print(name) names = name.split('_') print(names) re = names[0] + '-ethiopic' other = names[1] comp1 = GSComponent(re) comp2 = GSComponent(other) layer.components.append(comp1) layer.components.append(comp2) # gap = 100 # layer.components[1].transform = (( # 1, # x scale factor # 0.0, # x skew factor # 0.0, # y skew factor # 1, # y scale factor # gap, # x position # 0.0 # y position # ))
# copies all componets across layers, one instance must be open from makkeblue script menju
font = Glyphs.font for layer in font.selectedLayers: lyrs = layer.parent.layers regular = lyrs[1] bold = lyrs[0] thin = lyrs[2] CopyLayerToLayer().copyComponentsFromLayerToLayer(regular, bold) CopyLayerToLayer().copyComponentsFromLayerToLayer(regular, thin)
# if needed disable autoalignment and fix bearings # dont forgetto set these values, newRSB, newLSB, low, top font = Glyphs.font
newRSB = 60 newLSB = 60 low = 0 top = 133 for layer in font.selectedLayers: # print(layer.LSB, layer.RSB, layer.parent.name ) if (layer.RSB < low): name = layer.parent.name comp = GSComponent(name) isAutoAligned = comp.automaticAlignment print('fix low rsb......: ', name) if isAutoAligned: for comp in layer.components: comp.setDisableAlignment_(True) print(comp) layer.RSB = newRSB
if (layer.LSB < low): name = layer.parent.name comp = GSComponent(name) isAutoAligned = comp.automaticAlignment print('fix low LSB...: ', name) if isAutoAligned: for comp in layer.components: comp.setDisableAlignment_(True) print(comp) layer.LSB = newLSB
if (layer.LSB > top): name = layer.parent.name comp = GSComponent(name) isAutoAligned = comp.automaticAlignment print('fix top LSB...: ', name) if isAutoAligned: for comp in layer.components: comp.setDisableAlignment_(True) print(comp) layer.LSB = top
if (layer.RSB > top): name = layer.parent.name comp = GSComponent(name) isAutoAligned = comp.automaticAlignment print('fix top RSB...: ', name) if isAutoAligned: for comp in layer.components: comp.setDisableAlignment_(True) print(comp) layer.RSB = top
